➜在流感之后，肺炎链球菌会夺命——接种疫苗要趁早！
https://pansci.asia/archives/195069	3600
<ul> Care Online </a>喔</li></ul>
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img width="560" height="293" src="http://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b0552d31dfbfb86a05f27ba8d73fe356-560x293.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-196017" srcset="https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b0552d31dfbfb86a05f27ba8d73fe356-560x293.jpg 560w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b0552d31dfbfb86a05f27ba8d73fe356-510x267.jpg 510w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b0552d31dfbfb86a05f27ba8d73fe356-273x143.jpg 273w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b0552d31dfbfb86a05f27ba8d73fe356-350x183.jpg 350w, https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/b0552d31dfbfb86a05f27ba8d73fe356.jpg 740w" sizes="(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px" /></figure>
<p>「医师，我今天一起床就全身痠痛、很没精神。」老先生乾咳了两声，无精打采地说。</p>
<p>「有流鼻水吗？」医师问。</p>
<p>「没有流鼻水。」老先生摇摇头，「不过身体热热的。」</p><div class="pansc-content"></script>
